title: [Bay's Watch, Rocky Path]
description: A well-kept stone path leads down the bluff at the base of the watchtower, splitting to double back along the bluff and continuing down to the rugged shore to the east.  The bustle of the city above fades as the sound of crashing surf echoes from the stone.

A well-kept stone path leads down the bluff at the base of the watchtower, splitting to double back along the bluff and continuing down to the rugged, night-misted shore to the east.  The faint bustle of the city above fades as the sound of crashing surf echoes from the stone.
paths: Obvious paths: southeast, northwest, up, down
